attributeSource.infoString2: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate David Winans & Associates

data.description:
Cute single story home. Original wood floors throughout except floating vinyl floors in kitchen and breakfast, tile in bathroom.  Nice picture window in the living room. TV brackets stay.  Gas range, butcher block counters and custom made island with stainless top in kitchen.  Many updated light fixtures.  Water heater 6 months old, roof 2020, windows 8 years old, new electric panel box and wiring, GFCI 2011, hot water plumbing updated and main line apex plumbing to house from the street.  Extra insulation in the attic, lots of storage in garage with shelving, metal covered 15x10 patio, shop is 30x25 with air and heat, shed, and gutters on front of the house.  Custom made bar in shop.
Seller's do not have a survey.
